Title: Rimmel London The Only 1 Lipstick 3.9 g(800 Under My Spell)

Line lips with Rimmel London Exaggerate lip liner to create the perfect base. Use a lip brush to apply this gorgeous all in one lipstick, this will give you much more control than applying straight from the stick, blot your lips using a tissue and layer on another coat, this sequence really helps to prevent your lipstick from bleeding, with a long lasting effect. The first lipstick of its kind, The Only 1 is set to challenge lipstick history. A unique multitasker, it excels in EVERYTHING you look for in a lippie. Discover intense, high-impact shades. Title: Ralph Lauren Polo Black EDT  -  30 ml(For Men)
Description: Mysterious, enigmatic and provocative, the scent of Polo Black from the fashion house of Ralph Lauren stands out through its complex versatility. A confluence of elegant woody aromatic accords, this Eau de Toilette defines the charismatic charm of a gentleman through its elegant, gourmand notes. Created by perfumers Ellen Molner and Pierre Negrin, Polo Black opens with a sparkling top note of fresh, clean mango bouquet and Spanish sage infused with a hint of green effervescence. An opulent heart note of silver armoise and hedione trails into an intensely spicy, masculine base note of patchouli noir, sandal wood, timberol and tonka bean. A heady elixir that captivates the senses with daring, vibrant accords, the essence of Polo Black is as perfect for office wear as it is for a night on the town.

Title: Guerlain Aqua Allegoria Herba Fresca EDT  -  125 ml(For Men, Women)
Dunhill Pursuit EDT  -  50 ml(For Men)
Description: Dunhill Pursuit with a blend of a variety of spices, form a sensual scent fit for the man who is perennially in search of a thrilling experience. With fresh and woody ingredients, this luxury perfume exudes a scent of dauntless spirit that has you prepared to take on anything that comes your way. This complex Eau de Toilette was created by Michel Girard for the acclaimed house of Dunhill. The top note is filled with summery and ripe extracts of pineapple leaf, orange leaf, mandarin, yuzu, bergamot and green accords. The heart note comes with an assortment of extracts like spicy cinnamon and pepper with delicate cardamom, sweet and dry amber and floral lavender. This leads to the base note which has a stronger scent profile with smoky musk, woody cedar, warm sandalwood, earthy vetiver, amber and fragrant incense. The distinctive smell of this fragrance becomes a part of you and can be worn at any time of the day regardless of the season. The compact and rectangular glass vial built under the craftsmanship ofÂ  Franz â Rudolf Lehnert looks simple and refined. The stark transparency of the crystal clear glass wonderfully complements the saffron coloured, spice-laden perfume. A spritz of Dunhill Pursuit is the finishing touch before embarking on the ultimate adventure.

Title: Police New York EDT  -  50 ml(For Men)

D&G 1 Le Bateleur EDT - 100 ml(For Men)
Description: His nature does not allow him to mince words; direct and relentlessly so, he is one who is not afraid to fight for what he wants. Le Bateleur 1 from the fashion house of Dolce&Gabbana reminds him of why he is who he is. His cares with the heart of a baby and hates with the passion of a killer; the depth of his emotions distinguishes him from the world and this luxury Eau de Toilette is his constant companion. Spicy cardamom fuses lightly with juniper berries and birch to make for a mysterious top note. The crumbly heart note of coriander trails into the verdancy of vetiver mingled delicately with the dry, woodsy cedar. This base note is held down with the incense-like quality of olibanum that lends a smokiness to the fragrance inducing memories of dark, misty nights spent by the fireplace. This passionately playful essence is bound by the simplicity of a delicately crafted bottle emblazoned with the brand logo. Torrid heat wars with aquatic chills to make a man who is not afraid to play for high stakes and win.

Yardley Elegance is the perfect aftershave for the man who is worldly-wise.
